            "title": "港股開市︱初段微跌 恒指跌1點報25976點 中信証券績後高開1.2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股開市初段未能跟隨外圍揚升，恒生指數開市報25976點，微跌1點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報4929點，升27點或0.56%；國企指數以8788點開市，升12點或0.15%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_HKEX_FB.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股互有升跌，滙控(00005)開報139.6元，跌0.29%；友邦(01299)開報81元，跌0.8%。阿里巴巴(09988)開報131.8元，暫時無升跌；騰訊(00388)開報490元，跌0.69%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">多家公司相繼公布今年首季業績，中國神華盈利倒退逾11%，該股今早開報47.5元，跌0.71%；國藥(01099)盈利減少不足3%，該股今早開報19.41元，升0.99%；中興通訊(00763)盈利跌逾46%，該股今早開報23.82元，跌1.73%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：國藥官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230821_FI_source-web_國藥2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：國藥官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230821_FI_source-web_國藥2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：國藥官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中信証券(06030)首季盈利升逾54%，該股今早開報26.94元，升1.2%；赤峰黃金(06693)季度盈利翻一番，該股今早開報39.08元，升0.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">藥明康德(02359)將於今日派首季成績表，該股今早開報123.8元，升0.08%。</p>\n</div>",
